        "body" : "Yes, [here](https://cmake.org/cmake/help/git-master/command/cmake_minimum_required.html#command:cmake_minimum_required). The warnings are about CMake using old policy settings (specifically for the visibility policy). The recommended way is to avoid setting specific policies to NEW, and instead set the oldest version of CMake supported and the newest version of CMake tested (3.11, in this case). The if statement below is used if CMake < 3.12.",
